Description:
	Smashtein Garbage is a Super Smash Bros Brawl-like battle game.


Date:
	2010-01-18


Dependencies:
    sudo apt-get install libboost-graph-dev libqt4-dev freeglut3-dev libglew-dev libxmu-dev libxi-dev
    git clone git@github.com:libglui/glui.git
    cd glui
    cmake .
    make -j4
    sudo make install
	# install OpenKN => git@github.com:highronn/OpenKN.git
    # source there: http://igm.univ-mlv.fr/~boutarel/okn/math/files.html


Install fmod 32bits:
	cd lib
	tar xvzf fmodapi42805linux.tar.gz
	cd fmodapi42805linux
	sudo make install

OR

Install fmod 64bits:
	cd lib
	tar xvzf fmodapi42805linux64.tar.gz
	cd fmodapi42805linux64
	sudo make install


How-to compile and launch the game:
	cd Arena
	qmake
	make run
